6. Hide sensitive info from employees
In attendance/views.py, strip the IP address 
from employee-facing views.
 In attendance_history_view the template shouldn't show IP —
  make sure history.html doesn't display record.ip_address.

My recommendation — do these in this order:

Session security (settings.py changes — 2 minutes) ✅ easiest
Rate limiting (django-axes — 5 minutes) ✅ most impactful
Password strength (already built into Django) ✅ easy
Logging (good for auditing who did what)